OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FITV News is travelling with him and
OL,7,Fover the next few hours, his uncle
OL,8,Fshares Ahmad's story. It soon becomes
OL,9,Fclear that it is also the story of
OL,10,Fthis war, from the very first night it
OL,11,Fhit Gaza.
OL,13,FIn the northeastern town of Beit
OL,14,FHanoun, Ahmad, known for his cheeky
OL,15,Fsmile, is starting to get excited
OL,16,Fabout his first day at nursery.
OL,18,FHe is looking forward to joining his
OL,19,Fbig brother Mohammed on the daily walk
OL,20,Fto school.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/14
