OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FAs news of Hamas' assault on Israel
OL,7,Fbegins to emerge, the Shabbat family,
OL,8,Flike everyone else in Gaza, brace for
OL,9,FIsrael's response.
OL,11,FWith no bomb shelter, we don't know if
OL,12,Fthey are asleep when their home is one
OL,13,Fof the first to be hit in the early
OL,14,Fhours of October 8.
OL,16,FWhat we do know is that, despite the
OL,17,Fdesperate attempts of the emergency
OL,18,Fservices - which are still fully
OL,19,Ffunctioning on that first night -
OL,20,FAhmad's mother, father and brother are
OL,21,Fgone.
