OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FAhmad calls repeatedly for his mum,
OL,7,FDiana, as the Israeli bombardment
OL,8,Fintensifies.
OL,10,FBy October 10, Beit Hanoun, the only
OL,11,Fplace Ahmed has ever called home, is
OL,12,Funrecognisable.
OL,14,FThe Israel Defence Forces (IDF) drop
OL,15,Fleaflets from the sky, warning those
OL,16,Fleft to move to safer areas.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/14
