OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FSaleh is aged 26 and has just got
OL,7,Fengaged to be married. He is set to
OL,8,Fbecome Ahmad's guardian and primary
OL,9,Fcarer.
OL,11,FOn November 13, the pair walk to the
OL,12,Fmarket to try to buy food. It's the
OL,13,Flast time Ahmad walks anywhere.
OL,15,FThe stalls are hit by an Israeli
OL,16,Fmissile which blows off the three-year-
OL,17,Fold's legs.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/14
