OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FHis uncle Saleh cannot keep the
OL,7,Fpromise he's made to raise Ahmad as
OL,8,Fhis own because he doesn't survive the
OL,9,Fblast.
OL,11,FAt Gaza's Al Aqsa hospital, surgeons
OL,12,Fexhausted by five weeks of treating
OL,13,Fthe wounded manage to save Ahmad's
OL,14,Flife.
OL,16,FThey have no choice but to amputate
OL,17,Fhis legs at the thigh before he's
OL,18,Fmoved to a bed in a hospital corridor.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/14
