OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FIt is impossible to comfort the little
OL,7,Fboy who has lost everyone he loves and
OL,8,Fis in unimaginable pain.
OL,10,FBut his uncle Ibrahim tries, stroking
OL,11,Fhis nephew's hair as he cries out in
OL,12,Fpain.
OL,14,FIt takes almost two weeks to get Ahmad
OL,15,Fout of Gaza - doctors say if he stays
OL,16,Fhe has little chance of surviving.
OL,18,FIbrahim has to make the agonising
OL,19,Fdecision to leave his wife and one-and-
OL,20,Fa-half year old daughter behind to get
OL,21,Fhis nephew out.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/14
