OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FOnly after a direct plea to Egypt's
OL,7,Fpresident are the pair allowed to
OL,8,Fcross and head for a hospital that can
OL,9,Fhelp them in Cairo.
OL,11,FSomehow, thanks to the love and care
OL,12,Fof his uncle and the doctors and
OL,13,Fnurses who tend to his injuries, Ahmad
OL,14,Fstarts smiling again.
OL,16,FHe loves to race around the hospital
OL,17,Fcorridors, using a joystick to
OL,18,Fnavigate his new electric wheelchair,
OL,19,Fspeeding down hospital corridors.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/14
