OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FAhmad needs prosthetic legs and Italy
OL,7,Fhas offered to take him in and provide
OL,8,Fhim with medical care, after the UK
OL,9,FHome Office refused him entry.
OL,11,FFor a boy who's brushed so close to
OL,12,Fdeath, Ahmad is bursting with life and
OL,13,Fmischief. But he still asks for his
OL,14,Fmum and sometimes screams at his uncle
OL,15,Fthat he wants his old legs back.
OL,17,FIbrahim always calms him with cuddles,
OL,18,Fwhispering "It'll be alright, habibti".
