OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FThe years ahead will be full of
OL,7,Fpainful surgeries and Ahmad will have
OL,8,Fto face them without the parents he
OL,9,Floved so much by his side.
OL,11,FGiven all that he's lost it's
OL,12,Fimpossible to describe him as lucky.
OL,14,FBut he is at least safe now, unlike so
OL,15,Fmany children like him, still trapped
OL,16,Fin Gaza and struggling to survive.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G13/14
